title: Ability FTP server 2.34 vulnerable buffer overflow
description:
After scouring google and almost giving up... seeing as how everyone posting in forums was like "wtf where is ability server 2.34??"

..well, I finally found this in an arabic website!

And I downloaded it, thinking for sure it was going to be a rootkit, but nope.

It's actually the trial version of ability ftp server 2.34 and it's still vulnerable to the buffer overflow simple-fuzzer.py :)

Have fun!
